    {
      "instruction": "<p>Dissolve the <strong>chicken stock mix</strong>,<strong> red wine vinegar</strong>,<strong> wholegrain mustard </strong>and 1 tsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> [2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar </strong>in 150ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[250ml]</span><strong> boiled water </strong>–<strong> </strong>this is your<strong> mustard stock</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
