    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the pork steaks are done, transfer them to a chopping board or shallow plate, cover with a clean tea towel and leave them to rest until serving</p><p>Reserve the pan and any<strong> pork juices</strong> for the next step</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
