    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the pan to a medium-low heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>mustard stock </strong>to the pan and cook for 3-4 min</p><p>Increase the heat to medium-high, add a large knob of <strong>butter</strong> and cook for 1-2 min or until thickened to creamy consistency</p><p>Once thickened, remove from the heat and stir in the <strong>reserved</strong> <strong>pork juices</strong> – this is your <strong>mustard sauce</strong></p>",
